<sect1 id="sect_buildApplication" label="3">
    <title id="title_buildApplication">Build the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application happyHome</title>
    <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup rowsep="0" cols="2" align="left" colsep="0">
            <colspec colwidth="1*"/>
            <colspec colwidth="3*"/>
            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry/>
                    <entry rowsep="1"/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Intention</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>With the completion of the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application
                            design we are ready for a first built of our example application happyHome.</para>
                        <para>The creation of a <trademark>jACOB</trademark> project implies the
                            generation of a <guilabel>build.xml</guilabel> file. This file is
                            located in the project's root directory:</para>
                        <para>
                            <figure id="fig_buildXML">
                                <title id="title_fig_buildXML"> build.xml file</title>
                                <screenshot>
                                    <mediaobject>
                                        <imageobject>
                                            <imagedata fileref="./Screenshots/ProjectStructure.jpg"
                                                format="JPEG" scalefit="1" width="200" depth="100"/>
                                        </imageobject>
                                    </mediaobject>
                                </screenshot>
                            </figure>
                        </para>
                        <para>The file <guilabel>build.xml</guilabel> is an Ant file which contains
                            the target <guilabel>all</guilabel>. With the aid of this target we will
                            create a deployable <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application file.</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Procedure</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para> To do this perform the following steps: </para>
                        <para>
                            <informaltable rowsep="1" colsep="1" frame="all">
                                <tgroup cols="2">
                                    <colspec align="center" colwidth="1*"/>
                                    <colspec align="left" colwidth="6*"/>
                                    <thead>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>Step</entry>
                                            <entry align="center">Procedure</entry>
                                        </row>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>1</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>Select the file <guilabel>build.xml</guilabel>
                                                  in the <guilabel>Package Explorer</guilabel>.</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>2</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>Choose <guimenuitem>Run</guimenuitem> -
                                                  <guimenuitem>Ant Build...</guimenuitem> from
                                                  the right mouse button menu.</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>3</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>Select the target <guilabel>all</guilabel> in
                                                  the dialog window and initiate the built by
                                                  pressing the button <guibutton>Run</guibutton>.</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                    </tbody>
                                </tgroup>
                            </informaltable>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Impact</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>Hereafter, the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application file
                            <guilabel>happyHome-0.1.jacapp</guilabel> is generated in the newly
                            created directory <guilabel>dist</guilabel>:</para>
                        <para>
                            <figure id="fig_projectStructureAfterBuild">
                                <title>
                                    <trademark>jACOB</trademark> project structure after the built
                                    of the application</title>
                                <screenshot>
                                    <mediaobject>
                                        <imageobject>
                                            <imagedata
                                                fileref="./Screenshots/ProjectStructureAfterBuilt.jpg"
                                                format="JPEG" scalefit="1" width="200" depth="143"/>
                                        </imageobject>
                                    </mediaobject>
                                </screenshot>
                            </figure>
                        </para>
                        <para>The file <guilabel>happyHome-0.1.jacapp</guilabel> can be deployed
                            with help of the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> Admin application now (see
                            <trademark>jACOB</trademark> Admin Manual).</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Next Step</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>The next step will be to:</para>
                        <para>
                                                        <xref linkend="sect_defineTableHooks" endterm="title_defineTableHooks"/>

                        </para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry/>
                    <entry/>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
